RECICLADO DE MENU OPTIONS


--- Start Game
         1- Ask for names and position (Frontline or Backline).
         2- Ask for challenge rating.
         3- Ask if they want to decide enemies or if they should be randomly generated.
         4- Ask for map size?


--- Create New Monster
         1- Set name.
         2- Set stats.
         3- Set challenge rating? (This should be determined by the system, but it's probably really tough)
         4- Set gear / abilities.
         5- SET BEHAVIOUR.

